.idea folder is basically generated by the intellij idea for the track of settings
.mvn - its maven wrapper
static folder is used for storing the static files like storing the image .
api - application programming interface
restcontroller automatically convert java objects into json data

pojo - plain old java objects
when we are not extending and implementing framework class
jackson behind the scene converts the java objects into json , in the spring boot

postman/browser -> tomcat -> dispatcherServlet -> handlerMapping -> controller ->spring mvc ->httpmessageconverter -> desired format ->response tomcat

